data.description: This charming property offers a serene living experience, perfectly situated on a spacious lot with the scenic Classen-Steubing Ranch Park as its backdrop. The absence of rear neighbors enhances the sense of privacy and tranquility, while direct backyard access to the park invites nature and recreation right to your doorstep. The lower level of the home features an open floor plan, ideal for modern living. This layout encourages a seamless flow between living, dining, and kitchen areas, making it perfect for entertaining or spending quality time with family.
